http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\"}, {\"begin\": 624, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Ayers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tim Ayers\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Ayers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Ayers\"}, {\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomatic_Security_Service\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.218443018888631e-15, \"text\": \"DSS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomatic_Security_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomatic_Security_Service\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"safety and security information\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"any kind\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 475}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"terrorist threats\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"information\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"even weather-related issues\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"director\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"major events coordination\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ayers' team has been preparing for the Olympics for three years, working closely with French authorities and international partners, exchanging key information about security with one goal in mind: keeping American athletes and fans safe.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6657531075338152, \"rank\": 0.4134218155214184, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999826955915, \"rank\": 1.714494782935948e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ayers' team\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"international partners\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"key information\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"one goal\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are looking out for the safety and security of the U.S. athletes, but the best way to do that is to make sure the entire games are safe,\\\" Ayers said.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the safety\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. athletes\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"the best way\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire games\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"Ayers\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The task involves having agents live in the host city ahead of the Olympics and creating a partnership aimed at identifying vulnerabilities and strengths.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The task\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"agents\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"the host city\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"a partnership\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1182}, {\"ngram\": \"vulnerabilities\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"strengths\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Two agents out here brought back French security authorities to the Super Bowl in Phoenix a couple years ago, they brought them out to the U.N. General Assembly, they brought them out to the New Year's Eve celebration in New York to kind of show them how we do major events in the United States,\\\" Ayers said.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1270, \"end\": 1276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6657531075338152, \"rank\": 0.4134218155214184, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Suns\", \"score\": 0.8385007553898932, \"rank\": 0.14572860845153787, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Suns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Suns\"}, {\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9996698891141806, \"rank\": 0.0003282429181442092, \"text\": \"U.N.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_General_Assembly\", \"score\": 0.9999999921690232, \"rank\": 5.300569314604379e-09, \"text\": \"General Assembly\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_General_Assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_General_Assembly\"}, {\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999993137862556, \"rank\": 5.524016219435481e-07, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9994413997815419, \"rank\": 0.0005589123171223287, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Two agents\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"the Super Bowl\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"the New Year's Eve celebration\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"major events\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"Ayers\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ayers said one of his top concerns is a lone wolf attack.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lone_wolf_attack\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"lone wolf attack\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lone_wolf_attack\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lone_wolf_attack\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ayers\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"his top concerns\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You can watch everything, you can have your resources out there, but if somebody makes a decision to do something, it's going to be up to them and that's up to the French state to really respond to that,\\\" Ayers said.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1771, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6657531075338152, \"rank\": 0.4134218155214184, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"your resources\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1660}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1704}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"Ayers\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What we will do though is we will try and circle up and make sure those U.S. athletes are safe.\\\"\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those U.S. athletes\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another worry is a security meltdown from a cyberattack.\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another worry\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"a security meltdown\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"a cyberattack\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have put together the resources to try and look after any kind of cyberattacks and strengthen cyber defenses,\\\" Ayers said.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the resources\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"any kind\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"cyberattacks\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"cyber defenses\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"Ayers\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"However, as you saw with CrowdStrike, any kind of cyber incident that debilitated flights going all over the United States and overseas, it is something that's concerning, but we have tried to put together all the resources we can and we are working with the French government to exchange resources to make sure that we are all on top of it to try and identify it before it happens.\\\"\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2134, \"end\": 2145, \"